title: Batman - Streets of Gotham (01 - 21) (2009 - 2011) (complete)
description:
Batman - Streets of Gotham (01 - 21) (2009 - 2011) (complete) 

All scans from Minutemen



Batman: Streets of Gotham

Starring: Dick Grayson, Damian Wayne, Bruce Wayne and Hush

Second Feature: Manhunter ( #1-#13) Two Face ( #14,#16) Ragman ( #17-18.)

This series has been canceled by DC with #21 to be the last issue.

This series is also collected in trade paperbacks:

Hush Money (#1-4 w/ Detective Comics #852 & Batman #685)

Leviathan (#5-11) &

House of Hush (#12-14, 16-21)
